function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Walk npc offscreen and delete
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_Villager)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, marker_Villager_MoveTo, "npc_walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idClone, 2.0)
	end
end
